claim.claim-text:
A harvester comprising:
a frame (301) positioned around at least a first pair of side walls that define at least a first bale chamber (302);
a first and second subframe (330, 320) that define a compartment (310) within the harvester at a first operable position;
a net wrapping mechanism (500) positioned at least partially within the compartment;
a panel that facilitates access to the net wrapping mechanism (500) from a point exterior to the frame (301) and covers at least one interior portion of the compartment (310);
wherein the first subframe (330) is operably connected to the second subframe (320) and at least one of the first (330) or second subframes (320) is movable to at least a second operable position such that the second operable position of the first or second subframes (330,320) facilitates access to at least the one interior portion of the compartment (310) through the panel from a point exterior to the compartment (310).
